Package org.gbif.common.search.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HighlightableList
    A simple facade allowing a property to be a list of complex objects that can be treated as a simple String list for search highlighting.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FacetField.Method
    Indicates what type of algorithm/method to use when faceting a field.
    FacetField.SortOrder
    Valid sort orders.
    WildcardPadding
    WildcardPadding pattern for full text searches.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    FacetField
    Annotation that defines a faceted field.
    Field
    Annotation that defines a field mapping between a java or generic field and a schema field.
    FullTextSearchField
    Annotates setter methods of fields that can be used as part of the full text search.
    Key
    Defines a unique identification field.
    SearchMapping
    Annotation that defines a list of faceted fields.
    SuggestMapping
    Annotation used for suggest/autocomplete services.
